title: AJK president, CM GB witness proceedings of NA
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 03 (APP):Azad Jammu and Kashmir President Masood Khan along with Chief Minister of Gilgit-Baltistan Hafiz Hafeezur Rehman on Monday witnessed the proceedings of the National Assembly.
National Assembly Speaker Asad Qaiser made the announcement about presence of AJK President, Chief Minister Gilgit-Baltistan, Speaker AJK Legislative Assembly Shah Ghulam Qadir and Governor Gilgit-Baltistan Raja Jalal Hussain Maqpoon.
Members of National Assembly welcomed the visiting guests by thumping the desks.
Earlier, State Minister for Parliamentary Affairs Ali Muhammad Khan moved motion to suspend the normal business of the National Assembly so that house could hold debate on Kashmir issue.
